<C>__{wesley }
<D>__{perfect match on the description.}
<B>__{on charlie}
<A>__{lying across the front seat taping the reassembled photo of betty to the dash. charlie's beginning to come apart. his hair is uncombed and his clothes are wrinkled. his eyes have a thousand yard stare.}
